@startuml
title Sequence Diagram - Khóa/Mở khóa tài khoản khách hàng

actor Admin
participant "AdminCustomerController" as Ctrl
participant "CustomerService" as Svc
participant "UserRepository" as UserRepo
database "Database" as DB

Admin -> Ctrl: POST /admin/customers/toggle-status/{id}
activate Ctrl

Ctrl -> Svc: toggleUserStatus(userId)
activate Svc

Svc -> UserRepo: findById(userId)
activate UserRepo
UserRepo --> Svc: User entity
deactivate UserRepo

Svc -> Svc: Cập nhật status (ACTIVE <-> LOCKED)
Svc -> UserRepo: save(user)
activate UserRepo
UserRepo -> DB: UPDATE users SET status = ? WHERE id = ?
DB --> UserRepo: success
UserRepo --> Svc: void
deactivate UserRepo

Svc --> Ctrl: void
deactivate Svc

Ctrl --> Admin: Trả về thông báo cập nhật thành công
deactivate Ctrl

@enduml